# Tests

Follow `testing-conventions` (`.cursor/skills/testing-conventions/SKILL.md`).

- Colocate `.test.ts` in `src/lib/` — no `__tests__/` folders
- Fixtures in `src/_mock/`; mock services with `vi.mock('$lib/serv/...')`
- E2E in `e2e/` with POM classes in `e2e/_pom/`
- No `.only` in committed tests
